    "description": "Saving healer is a battle simulator logic game where you need to finish an ambush of enemies in just one turn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/05978d24ffc14cb3357d44ad9afda79a.poster.avif?t=1673296070\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/05978d24ffc14cb3357d44ad9afda79a.webm?t=1673296070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/05978d24ffc14cb3357d44ad9afda79a.mp4?t=1673296070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game's story is based on the quest to save the healer, a member of the group who was kidnapped by a band of bandits. The group then rallies to rescue their comrade, but the bandits are already waiting and everywhere the adventurers pass the bandits try to finish off the group in an ambush.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/2e0e8046575f0d138afc98ad13f2608d.poster.avif?t=1673296070\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/2e0e8046575f0d138afc98ad13f2608d.webm?t=1673296070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/2e0e8046575f0d138afc98ad13f2608d.mp4?t=1673296070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Hey, before you add it to your wish list, know that this is an indie game, developed by a guy in his house. This game is based on small fases of logic and observation, its not long but it takes a while for you to get past the fase.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/21b5c26873dd34067b93976102768c49.poster.avif?t=1673296070\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/21b5c26873dd34067b93976102768c49.webm?t=1673296070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173190/extras/21b5c26873dd34067b93976102768c49.mp4?t=1673296070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What this game has to offer: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 Unique Puzzles.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intuitive gameplay.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A minimalist and relaxing atmosphere.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>14 Amazing sound tracks.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>14 Beautiful levels.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What this game does <u>NOT</u> have to offer: </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turn-Base Strategy.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Character Leveling.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Skill cards.</li></ul>",
